{
  "id": "RAW_0ae973c9",
  "title": "浮世绘风格",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMzc1NzM1Mw==&mid=2247484942&idx=1&sn=57d4bc0e2435c709fbdba5db2b1b11a0",
  "date": "2025-12-30 02:09:00",
  "author": "李继刚",
  "siteName": "李继刚",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f84f5d7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpXxH8kJhw0yllZiaK3u0T080nhladtYF90iblMaDPfOhWrI5WKibxbrSiaw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\" margin: 0px auto;line-height: 1.3;max-width: 80%;text-align: center !important;font-weight: 600 !important;color: rgb(29, 29, 31) !important; padding-bottom: 0.5em !important;font-size: 2.2em !important;letter-spacing: -0.02em !important; \" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">浮世绘风格</span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:28.7969px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 作者: 李继刚</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑名: 浮世绘风格</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑意: 生成浮世绘风格的画面</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; date: 2025-12-29</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">风格调性</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Keywords: Shin-hanga (新版画风格), Ukiyo-e Aesthetics (浮世绘美学), Serene Melancholy, Atmospheric landscape, Traditional Japanese Art.</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Description: 画面呈现出 20 世纪初日本“新版画”运动的典型特征，结合了传统浮世绘的木刻技法与西方印象派的光影氛围。整体气质静谧、孤寂且充满诗意。核心在于捕捉特定的气候氛围与瞬间的静止感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">视觉逻辑</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Perspective: 散点透视与高视点结合。非严格的西方单点透视，强调平面的纵深感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Composition: 强烈的对角线构图，利用大面积留白与实体景物形成虚实对比。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Geometry: 有机线条与几何色块的叠加。景物边缘清晰但不过度锐利，呈现出版画特有的刻刀雕琢感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">视觉渲染</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Line Work: 墨线轮廓，线条粗细变化模仿毛笔笔触，但在建筑和树枝细节上保持木刻的刚劲。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Texture: 显著的和纸纹理，利用纸张原本的白色作为高光。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Technique: Bokashi: 在水面和天空中使用渐变印染技法，表现色彩的柔和过渡。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Goma-zuri: 局部可能存在的“胡麻摺”效果，产生颗粒感以模拟降雪或质感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Lighting: 漫射光。无明确光源方向，通过色块明度差异表现积雪的厚度与阴天光感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">色彩系统</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Prussian Blue / Indigo (<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjry1v6y-8rcvtb\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#1B365D</a>): 用于水面渐变，深邃且沉静。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Slate Grey (<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjry1v6y-h4sk52\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#708090</a>): 用于天空与阴影，营造寒冷氛围。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Paper White / Cream (<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjry1v6y-78a1jq\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#F5F5DC</a>): 画布底色，直接指代积雪。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Charcoal Black (<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjry1v6y-anlvbx\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#36454F</a>): 用于树木与建筑剪影。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Core Logic: 低饱和度，冷色调主导，极简主义配色。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Palette:</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">负向约束</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁照片级真实感、物理渲染</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁数字绘画的光滑感、高光反射、塑料质感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁厚涂笔触、油画堆叠感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁体积光、环境光遮蔽等现代 3D 渲染技法。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁使用鲜艳、高纯度的霓虹色或原色。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大雪天气，《鬼灭之刃》所有「柱」的定妆照，每个「柱」都按自己的呼吸法做战斗准备姿势。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">居中位置是主角灶門炭治郎和弥豆子</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001286\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ab2b650&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42Jpo4uziazqAjn4f2aDD9jCYQbAyay21427KCe7qvERIM4Uia3haWL8KcMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">将「画面内容」部分做替换即可保持画风，生成自己需要的画面内容：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">「</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">千山鳥</span></span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">飛絕</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，. 萬徑人蹤滅。 孤舟蓑笠翁，. 獨釣寒江雪。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001287\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5a275f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpeDbM1jgrdzxXYic1MgHic9CqVgawImljsJ4jCqSQyiarcv5JzziclBKrUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">「</span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">十年生死兩茫茫</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不思量</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">自難忘</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">千里孤墳</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(255, 137, 126);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">無處話淒涼</span></em><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(191, 191, 191);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">。縱使相逢應不識，塵滿面，鬢如霜。 夜來幽夢忽還鄉，小軒窗，正梳妝。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001288\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c65b996e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpllsRSUcXaQHbE7iaBb6w0Ya8QAiaHwcj0V3rVttPmlUa6ib2tCicN4YZaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">将之前记录的一些读书笔记进行可视化：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001289\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1fb1aa10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpcSIxjSBAFQTGYdShLnUBicxAzSVVjzfj6FvxQ0bsq9m3yY91dzKjfNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001290\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee0967d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpslA1YjwkelVibgtD8Sq2OcYDx5gakHF3lFFqPhNVjRtaPsRdhkSnHWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001293\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d4dc1bef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9AP44b5pZdribdHj6tdC42JpaMEIIUibmN2NUZPIA6XMRPXVgra6COdAzHIOgOapkD1sFFkHMJewrqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细拆解浮世绘风格，提供一套用于文生图模型生成日式新版画风格画面的提示词策略，并展示其应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细拆解浮世绘风格，提供一套用于文生图模型生成日式新版画风格画面的提示词策略，并展示其应用。",
  "summary": "本文李继刚分享了一种浮世绘风格的 Midjourney (或其他文生图模型) 提示词策略，旨在生成具有 20 世纪初日本“新版画”特征的画面。作者详细拆解了这种风格的视觉要素，包括其静谧、孤寂的调性；散点透视与对角线构图的视觉逻辑；墨线轮廓、和纸纹理、渐变印染 (Bokashi) 和胡麻摺 (Goma-zuri) 的视觉渲染技术；以及由普鲁士蓝、石板灰、纸白、炭黑组成的低饱和度、冷色调色彩系统。文章还明确列出了为避免生成不符风格的画面而设定的负向约束，如严禁照片级真实感、数字绘画的光滑感和鲜艳色彩等。最后通过将此风格应用于动漫角色、古诗词意境和读书笔记可视化等不同内容，展示了该策略的通用性和生成效果，核心观点是将艺术风格解构成可复用的提示词模块。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "将复杂的艺术风格解构为可控的提示词要素，用于文生图模型。",
